<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Forget cached schemas and sync the data source again</b></p><p>If you see no objects below the schema level, cannot find changes in objects, experience broken tables or any other visualization problems, try to clear the cache and sync the data source again.</p><p>To clear the cache, right-click a data source and navigate to <span class="control">Diagnostics | Forget Cached Schemas</span>.</p></body></html>